data.description: Welcome to your contemporary 3-level 2-bd/2.5 ba townhouse in the heart of the vibrant Atlanta Airport District and popular City of Hapeville—offering a perfect blend of convenience and comfort! Can you imagine celebrating the new year in your new home? Well, this is your chance!  Greeted with beautiful hardwood floors, dual entry to the lower level from the front and back allows prime privacy and versatility for the bedroom and full bathroom to create a sleeping oasis, home office, wellness den, in-law, or rental suite. Continuing to the main level, an open layout seamlessly connects the spacious living, dining, and kitchen areas and includes a half bathroom. The well-appointed kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, sleek countertops, abundant storage and is strategically situated for the ultimate culinary and entertainment experiences. As you ascend to the third floor, the chic and roomy bedroom loft retreat provides a serene sanctuary and overlooks the lower level. The full-floor retreat features a custom closet, wardrobe nook, and full bathroom for you to experience ample relaxation and reprieve. Access to nature is amplified with your two private patios and courtyard, ideal for morning meditation and catching up with loved ones, and a two-car garage makes parking easy. Nestled minutes away from local food favorites, the bustling energy of the city and the world’s busiest airport, this gem is perfectly placed to help foodies, travelers and entertainment seekers create and celebrate memorable moments—make it yours!
